gory:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2010s Kannada-language films]]\n[[Category:Indian romance films]]\n[[Category:2010s romance films]]\n[[Category:Films directed by S. Narayan]]\n[[Category:Kannada films remade in other languages]]\n\n{{2010s-Kannada-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=October 2015}}\n{{Infobox film\n|name            = Appayya\n| image          = Appayya_(2013_film).jpg\n|director        = [[S. Narayan]]\n|producer        = Bhagyavathi Narayan<br>[[S. Narayan]]\n|starring        = [[Srinagar Kitty]]<br>[[Surabhi Prabhu]]<br>[[Bhama]]\n|music           = [[S. Narayan]]<br>Dharma Vish (background score)\n|cinematography  = Jagadish Wali\n|choreography    = \n|released        = {{Film date|df=yes|2013|09|13|ref=1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/kannada/article/97426.html|title=2 Films for 2 Days!|publisher=IndiaGlitz|accessdate=13 September 2013}}</ref>}}\n|studio          = Bhagyavathi Combines\n|editing         = \n|language        = Kannada\n|country         = India\n|budget          = \n}}\n\n'''''Appayya''''' ({{lang-kan|\u0c85\u0caa\u0ccd\u0caa\u0caf\u0ccd\u0caf}}) is a 2013 Kannada romance film written, directed and co-produced by [[S. Narayan]]. He has also scored the music for the film.  It is produced under Bhagyavathi Combines. [[Srinagar Kitty]] and [[Bhama]] are in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.supergoodmovies.com/44122/sandalwood/appayya-all-set-for-june-release-news-details|title='Appayya' all Set for June Release|date=4 May 2012|accessdate=9 May 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507024502/http://www.supergoodmovies.com/44122/sandalwood/appayya-all-set-for-june-release-news-details|archive-date=7 May 2012|url-status=dead}}</ref> All songs have been arranged and programmed by Dharma Vish who has also composed the background music.\n\nAfter much delay in finding the release date, the film finally made its premier across Karnataka on 13 September 2013.<ref>[http://www.indiaglitz.com/channels/kannada/article/97426.html 2 Films for 2 Days!]</ref> It was remade in [[Cinema of Bangladesh|Bangladeshi]] in 2016 as ''[[Angaar (2016 film)|Angaar]]'' starring with [[Om (actor)|Om]] and [[Falguni Rahman Jolly|Jolly]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://moviepagla.com/archives/1977|title=\u0985\u09a8\u09b2\u09be\u0987\u09a8\u09c7 \u2018\u0985\u0999\u09cd\u0997\u09be\u09b0\u2019 \u099b\u09ac\u09bf\u09b0 \u09ab\u09be\u09b0\u09cd\u09b8\u09cd\u099f \u09b2\u09c1\u0995 \u099f\u09bf\u099c\u09be\u09b0 \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u0995\u09be\u09b6 (\u09ad\u09bf\u09a1\u09bf\u0993 \u09b8\u09b9)|last=Mridul|first=Ahmed|date=14 November 2015|accessdate=6 March 2016}}</ref> thereby becoming the third Kannada film to be remade in Bangladeshi as well as the third Kannada movie to be remade in a foreign language after ''[[Anuraga Aralithu]]'' and ''[[Appu (2002 film)|Appu]]''.\n\n==Production==\n''Appayya'' for which he procured the story from a stranger in Bengaluru International airport by paying Rs.25000 stars Srinagara Kitty in the lead role with Bhama as counterpart. This is the real-life story completing shooting has finished the re-recording at sounDsiesigns Recording studio by Dharma Vish.\n\n==Cast==\n*[[Srinagar Kitty]] as Appayya\n*[[Surabhi Prabhu]]\n*[[Bhama]] \n*Indrakumar\n \n*Suresh Chandra\n*Asha Rani\n*[[S. Narayan]]\n\n==Soundtrack==\n\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Appayya\n| type       = [[Soundtrack]]\n| artist     = [[S. Narayan]]\n| cover      =\n| alt        =\n| released   = {{Start date|df=yes|2012|12|14}}\n| recorded   =\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Film soundtrack|Feature film soundtrack]]\n| length     = <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.southsongs4u.in/2012/12/appayya2012-kannada-movie-mp3-songs.html |title=Appayya(2012) Kannada Movie Mp3 Songs |date=15 December 2012 |accessdate=4 January 2013 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102025414/http://www.southsongs4u.in/2012/12/appayya