ck Porcello|Porcello]]''' (14\u201312) || [[Kolby Allard|Allard]] (4\u20132) || \u2014 || [[Globe Life Park in Arlington|Globe Life Park]] || 29,290 || 83\u201375 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2019/month_09/day_25/gid_2019_09_25_bosmlb_texmlb_1/boxscore_col.html W2]\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background-color:#fbb\"\n| 159 || Sep 26 || @ [[2019 Texas Rangers season|Rangers]]  || 5\u20137 || [[Mike Minor (baseball)|Minor]] (14\u201310) || '''[[Ryan Weber|Weber]]''' (2\u20134) || [[Jos\u00e9 Leclerc|Leclerc]] (14) || [[Globe Life Park in Arlington|Globe Life Park]] || 24,612 || 83\u201376 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2019/month_09/day_26/gid_2019_09_26_bosmlb_texmlb_1/boxscore_col.html L1]\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background-color:#fbb\"\n| 160 || Sep 27 || [[2019 Baltimore Orioles season|Orioles]]  || 1\u20134 || [[Asher Wojciechowski|Wojciechowski]] (4\u20138) || '''[[Nathan Eovaldi|Eovaldi]]''' (2\u20131) || \u2014 || '''[[Fenway Park]]''' || 34,533 || 83\u201377 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2019/month_09/day_27/gid_2019_09_27_balmlb_bosmlb_1/boxscore_col.html L2]\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background-color:#fbb\"\n| 161 || Sep 28 || [[2019 Baltimore Orioles season|Orioles]]  || 4\u20139 || [[John Means (baseball)|Means]] (12\u201311) || '''[[Jhoulys Chac\u00edn|Chac\u00edn]]''' (3\u201312) || \u2014 || '''[[Fenway Park]]''' || 36,414 || 83\u201378 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2019/month_09/day_28/gid_2019_09_28_balmlb_bosmlb_1/boxscore_col.html L3]\n|- style=\"text-align:center; background-color:#bfb\"\n| 162 || Sep 29 || [[2019 Baltimore Orioles season|Orioles]]  || 5\u20134 || '''[[Brandon Workman|Workman]]''' (10\u20131) || [[Dillon Tate|Tate]] (0\u20132) || \u2014 || '''[[Fenway Park]]''' || 35,427 || 84\u201378 || [https://gd2.mlb.com/content/game/mlb/year_2019/month_09/day_29/gid_2019_09_29_balmlb_bosmlb_1/boxscore_col.html W1]\n|}\n</div></div>\n'''Reference''':<ref name=\"schedulehalf1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/team/schedule/_/name/bos/season/2019/seasontype/2/half/1|title=Boston Red Sox Schedule - 2019|website=[[ESPN]]|accessdate=October 24, 2018|quote=First half}}</ref><ref name=\"schedulehalf2\">{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/team/schedule/_/name/bos/season/2019/seasontype/2/half/2|title=Boston Red Sox Schedule - 2019|website=[[ESPN]]|accessdate=October 24, 2018|quote=Second half}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Grand slams===\n[[File:Michael Chavis, Keon Broxton (48076090396) (cropped).jpg|thumb|right|upright|[[Michael Chavis]] (left) hit his first MLB grand slam on July 15.]]\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No. !! Date !! Red Sox batter !! H/A !! Pitcher !! Opposing team\n|-\n| 1 || April 20 || [[Andrew Benintendi]] || Away || [[Charlie Morton (pitcher)|Charlie Morton]] || Tampa Bay Rays\n|-\n| 2 || May 5 || [[Xander Bogaerts]] || Away || [[Juan Minaya]] || Chicago White Sox\n|-\n| 3 || July 15 || [[Michael Chavis]] || Home || [[Trent Thornton]] || Toronto Blue Jays\n|-\n| 4 || September 15 || [[Christian V\u00e1zquez]] || Away || [[Jason Vargas]] || Philadelphia Phillies\n|}\n\n===Ejections===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No. !! Date !! Red Sox personnel !! H/A !! Opposing team\n|-\n| 1 || rowspan=2|June 11 || [[Andrew Benintendi]] || rowspan=2|Home || rowspan=2|Baltimore Orioles\n|-\n| 2 || [[Alex Cora]]\n|-\n| 3 || July 25 || [[Brock Holt]] || Home || New York Yankees\n|-\n| 4 || rowspan=2|August 3 || Alex Cora || rowspan=2|Away || rowspan=2|New York Yankees\n|-\n| 5 || [[Chris Sale]]\n|}\n\n==Awards and honors==\n[[File:Rafael Devers.jpg|thumb|right|upright|[[Rafael Devers]] was named [[Major League Baseball Player of the Month Award|AL Player of the Month]] for May.]]\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#f7e1d7;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#c60c30; color:#FFF; border-top: 3px solid #024; border-bottom: 3px solid #024; border-left: 3px solid #024;\" width=\"5%\" | Recipient\n! style=\"